Establishment of regression-based normative isometric strength values for major 
lower limb muscle groups in persons with multiple sclerosis.

DelMastro HM(1), Simaitis LB(2), Gromisch ES(3), Gomes K(4), Ruiz JA(5).

Author information:
(1)Mandell Center for Multiple Sclerosis, Mount Sinai Rehabilitation Hospital, 
Trinity Health Of New England, 490 Blue Hills Avenue, Hartford, CT, 06112, 
United States; Department of Rehabilitative Medicine, Frank H. Netter MD School 
