Author information:
(1)Department of Biological Sciences, College of Science, King Faisal 
University, Al-Ahsa, 31982, Saudi Arabia.
(2)Centre of Molecular Medicine and Diagnostics (COMManD), Department of 
Biochemistry, Saveetha Dental College & Hospitals, Saveetha Institute of Medical 
