The efficacy of alendronate for the treatment of thalassemia-associated 
osteoporosis: a randomized controlled trial.

Piriyakhuntorn P(1), Tantiworawit A(1), Phimphilai M(2), Srichairatanakool S(3), 
Teeyasoontranon W(4), Rattanathammethee T(1), Hantrakool S(1), Chai-Adisaksopha 
C(1), Rattarittamrong E(1), Norasetthada L(1), Fanhchaksai K(5)(6), Charoenkwan 
